<paragraph id="F096836D5C6B79908E42C75175526F2C" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">Froelichs Thymian</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="0821FD95218E56DA55A9C01C50F7FD75" pageId="null" pageNumber="150" type="description">
<paragraph id="7A20FED75F1C85B61A8FF440AF5C36BC" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="2DB565B20DDDC656EAD2D4CDE1740A8A" class="Insecta" family="Eulophidae" genus="Thymus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="150" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pulegioides">
<emphasis id="7D28B44878BDB7D5A0948269B74ACE8B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">Th. pulegioides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 2e) durch folgende Merkmale: Pflanze in allen Teilen dichter und 
<normalizedToken id="0ADE1F90D45B46063C6FF680841D8FFB" originalValue="länger" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">laenger</normalizedToken>
behaart; 
<emphasis id="0D94E06AE479ADFF8A27C6888FCFBE8F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">
Haare der 
<normalizedToken id="A0163066D0845AFDF4A26744B0819BB5" originalValue="blühenden" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">bluehenden</normalizedToken>
Stengeltriebe meist 
<normalizedToken id="3BE0F67375A7A19C7D35D44B8872A130" originalValue="länger" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">laenger</normalizedToken>
als der Stengeldurchmesser
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="4941C9CD1A306B93818306698D7FA271" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">0,5</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="9B009BCC632E3A665A8DB17990DBC42C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">2 mm lang</emphasis>
), 
<emphasis id="BEA30B7CD29883BEE6A258DEF6DA8615" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">senkrecht abstehend.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="45B6201CE16A4E60BF58E7C22FED02B9" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
2-4mal so lang wie breit, 
<emphasis id="8FD8E9E5FE6E22EC33BBA0AE4D1E39DD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">beiderseits ziemlich dicht behaart.</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="285D52BD57BAD7D91E4F6632BBB8B1ED" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7DB93ABB5A0D7C6855A614A74CDDFD43" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">
<emphasis id="9429D6913E92AA6EC599E347AF3EB86D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="58302856D4B9D33F366E89216A3B66AE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">28:</emphasis>
Material aus dem Wallis (Pigott 1954), aus Frankreich (Bonnet 1961a).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="60DD5536F328B011666930A93B0C2A5D" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">
<emphasis id="45098D009FF7DAA761AA1AE76DD3B6E6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin, montan und subalpin. Trockene, oft kalkhaltige, magere, steinige 
<normalizedToken id="21ED32A80DB6B717F34631896DA40291" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. Trockenwiesen, Felsensteppen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="94B7F723FFF543F3A1FFAD4E4FEC2E4A" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">
<emphasis id="341DA24007491A43EA0F64A590C2D20D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="89FF575D4A08E2FB4CDD4C628F075CC8" originalValue="Westeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">Westeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
Westengland, 
<normalizedToken id="A8913E1C3C2FCBE05EAA32EB986E7EB8" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, Plateau Central, Alpen, 
<normalizedToken id="B9AE9978BE3E121A316BC4427EBBA5A0" originalValue="Südwestdeutschland" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">Suedwestdeutschland</normalizedToken>
, Tschechoslowakei, Norddeutschland (Wolgart), Osteuropa (?). (Verbreitungsangaben in Mitteleuropa von Roussine 1961). - Im Gebiet: Unterwallis, Oberrheinische Tiefebene, Nordschweiz, 
<normalizedToken id="524C81E297ED8CD25B7473C5C0E66A65" originalValue="Südschwarzwald" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">Suedschwarzwald</normalizedToken>
, Baar, Bodenseegebiet, Walenseegebiet; 
<normalizedToken id="E72AA93F29053EA35FAAFE9A4BE86FE4" originalValue="Alpensüdseite" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">Alpensuedseite</normalizedToken>
(
<normalizedToken id="7B2CC9F277D258B86C55D808B85B9B13" originalValue="südliches" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">suedliches</normalizedToken>
Tessin und angrenzende italienische Seengebiete, Misox, 
<normalizedToken id="830EA44879E3C6E13CCDF746B33FBCBF" originalValue="Münstertal" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">Muenstertal</normalizedToken>
); nicht 
<normalizedToken id="0554B7F8911B500469982C81F180BD77" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">haeufig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="30A8398CBC44929799C15913A71B1C7E" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">
<emphasis id="FE091DDBE7A9A926D769A534FBF11AC8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Jalas (1971) betrachtet 
<taxonomicName id="F77677F41F5F0F06C0EC13A861B23B62" class="Insecta" family="Eulophidae" genus="Thymus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="150" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="froelichianus">
<emphasis id="E707D01D224F71B06F12A22BFF6BDACF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">Th. Froelichianus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
nur als behaarte Form von 
<emphasis id="05918CC5FA277776B0227B93A0987F2E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="150">
<taxonomicName id="3B4A0094C9B1287FA6E39EFEB6D72B3D" class="Insecta" family="Eulophidae" genus="Thymus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="150" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pulegioides">Th. pulegioides</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
